--TEST--
a float literal lexes as a single TOKEN_NUMBER (fraction and exponent forms); '..' still splits integers for ranges
--ARGS--
--tokenize
--FILE--
3.14 1e9 2.5e-3 1..10 42
--EXPECT--
TOKEN_NUMBER(3.14) [1:1]
TOKEN_NUMBER(1e9) [1:6]
TOKEN_NUMBER(2.5e-3) [1:10]
TOKEN_NUMBER(1) [1:17]
TOKEN_DOT_DOT [1:18]
TOKEN_NUMBER(10) [1:20]
TOKEN_NUMBER(42) [1:23]
